    "description": "Experience the thrill of battle with the <strong>Letalis Demo</strong>! Dive into the first map zone and get a taste of the action, and the best part? Your progress carries over to the full game! Prepare for glory—your journey starts now!<br><br><strong>Explore a Non-Linear World</strong>:<br>Embark on a journey through diverse landscapes, facing fearsome enemies and towns in need as you seek the Colosseums to test your might.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/686bc7a97d6cdec54947337842158abd.poster.avif?t=1747175447\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/686bc7a97d6cdec54947337842158abd.webm?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/686bc7a97d6cdec54947337842158abd.mp4?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Glory or Death</strong>:<br>The clash of Letalis is a spectacle of raw power and unyielding determination. As they charge into battle, their shouts echo across the battlefield, fueled by adrenaline and the thirst for glory. With each swing of their mighty axes and swords, sparks fly and metal clashes, filling the air with the sound of combat. There is no shame of those who perish after a good match!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/a0787dcbce373fc7af9a6d7e39fba8cb.poster.avif?t=1747175447\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/a0787dcbce373fc7af9a6d7e39fba8cb.webm?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/a0787dcbce373fc7af9a6d7e39fba8cb.mp4?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Manage your Team</strong>:<br>Find the right balance of Fighting Styles betweem your Letalis lineup and gear them up with the right weapons to follow your strategy and enhance their combat abilities. Experiment with various combinations to suit your unique playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/3fcf904a0a39b86975ee43edf73fa87a.poster.avif?t=1747175447\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/3fcf904a0a39b86975ee43edf73fa87a.webm?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/3fcf904a0a39b86975ee43edf73fa87a.mp4?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Intense Colosseum Battles</strong>:<br>The real challenge to test your might! Three battles in row where every move could be your last. Study their patterns, exploit their lineups, and emerge triumphant against their Caesar.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/544d2d1558c405ec64847a595b022ad0.poster.avif?t=1747175447\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/544d2d1558c405ec64847a595b022ad0.webm?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/544d2d1558c405ec64847a595b022ad0.mp4?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Unlock World Mysteries</strong>:<br>Delve into the lives of citizens to unveil hidden secrets and gain insights into the intricate web of political intrigue that envelops the realm. As you peel back the layers of mystery, you'll uncover not only the machinations of power but also stumble upon long-forgotten dungeons teeming with untold riches and ancient artifacts waiting to be unearthed.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/571029ecb67d6065e75de4fcba351577.poster.avif?t=1747175447\" width=360 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/571029ecb67d6065e75de4fcba351577.webm?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262030/extras/571029ecb67d6065e75de4fcba351577.mp4?t=1747175447\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
